Text: I had to delete the other torrent, because I do not know why, utorrent started checking in alone and was 98.80%. As yet no one had done a full download, I decided to enter the torrent again. Sorry. Sorry for my bad English.

Maybe your previous torrent's content got changed during uploading. Make sure to make the content 'read only' before uploading (making .torrent file) till 100% seeding (having other seeders).
